Items.description: Larry Fitzgerald set up and scored the winning TD on the third play of OT, taking a 5-yard pass that lifted Arizona past Green Bay after Aaron Rodgers' 41-yard TD on the final play of regulation.
Items.vs: Arizona Cardinals vs. Green Bay Packers

Items.description: The Panthers built a 31-point halftime lead before barely holding off Seattle's relentless comeback to beat the Seahawks 31-24 on Sunday to advance to the NFC Championship Game.
Peyton Manning rescued the Broncos with a late touchdown drive, and Denver advanced to the AFC championship game with a 23-16 win over the Pittsburgh Steelers.
Peyton Manning is off and running. ... all the way to the Super Bowl, and he has the Broncos' defense to thank.
Items.vs: Denver Broncos vs. New England Patriots

Items.description: Cam Newton totaled four touchdowns, and Carolina's defense forced six turnovers to stifle Arizona's top-ranked offense in a 49-15 romp Sunday to win the NFC championship.

The 2016 Pro Bowl (branded as the 2016 Pro Bowl presented by USAA for sponsorship reasons) was the National Football League's all-star game for the 2015 season, which was played at Aloha Stadium in Honolulu, Hawaii on January 31, 2016.
Von Miller forced two fumbles to set up Denver's two touchdowns, and the Broncos' defense frustrated Cam Newton all game to carry Peyton Manning to his second Super Bowl win in a 24-10 victory.
